---
import Icon from '../icon-sprite';
import { Logo, Logos } from '../utilities/logo';
---

<section
  id="onetwentyone-section"
  class="flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-[40%_1fr] py-10 border-b max-h-screen"
>
  <div class="md:sticky md:top-48 md:self-start">
    <div class="px-8 border-l border-muted-foreground/30 flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <h1 class="font-mono font-bold md:text-3xl text-muted-foreground">OneTwentyOne</h1>
        <Logo name={Logos.OneTwentyOne} className="size-4.5" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground/80 uppercase font-mono mt-1"
      >
        <Icon name="pinCircle" className="size-3.5" />
        <p class="font-medium text-muted-foreground/80">Ithaca // San Francisco, 2023-</p>
      </div>
      <p class="font-medium text-muted-foreground/80 mt-2">Founder, CEO</p>
    </div>
    <div class="px-8 mt-4 text-muted-foreground/80 flex flex-col gap-2">
      <p>
        I started OneTwentyOne in 2023 after I got my first blood test, and noticed an abnormality
        my PCP didn't (high serum folate, high serum B12, high homocysteine â†’ functional B12
        deficiency from C677T homozygous mutation).
      </p>
      <p>
        We tried our hand at a mobile app first, but our real technical IP was in our data analysis
        and sync engine. In summer 2024, we partnered with Michael Lustgarten, Ph.D, to build <a
          href="https://conquer.onetwentyone.ai"
          class="underline">Conquer</a
        >, a biomarker analysis tool. Try it now!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hidden md:block h-auto">
    <div>
      <img src="/images/biomark-overview.webp" alt="121 Health" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
